    "chapter": 1,
    "verse": 3,
    "text": "Blessed\nbe the God and Father of our Lord Jesus Christ, which according to his abundant mercy hath begotten us again unto a lively hope by the resurrection of Jesus Christ from the dead,"
  },
  {
    "book": "1 Peter",
    "chapter": 1,
    "verse": 4,
    "text": "To an inheritance incorruptible, and undefiled, and that fadeth not away, reserved in heaven for you,"
  },
  {
    "book": "1 Peter",
