    "chapter": 1,
    "verse": 18,
    "text": "Forasmuch as ye know that ye were not redeemed with corruptible things,\nas silver and gold, from your vain conversation\nreceived\n by tradition from your fathers;"
  },
  {
    "book": "1 Peter",
    "chapter": 1,
    "verse": 19,
    "text": "But with the precious blood of Christ, as of a lamb without blemish and without spot:"
  },
  {
    "book": "1 Peter",
    "chapter": 1,
    "verse": 20,
    "text": "Who verily was foreordained before the foundation of the world, but was manifest in these last times for you,"
  },
  {
    "book": "1 Peter",
    "chapter": 1,
    "verse": 21,
    "text": "Who by him do believe in God, that raised him up from the dead, and gave him glory; that your faith and hope might be in God."
  },
  {
    "book": "1 Peter",
    "chapter": 1,
    "verse": 22,
    "text": "Seeing ye have purified your souls in obeying the truth through the Spirit unto unfeigned love of the brethren,\nsee that ye love one another with a pure heart fervently:"
  },
  {
    "book": "1 Peter",
    "chapter": 1,
    "verse": 23,
    "text": "Being born again, not of corruptible seed, but of incorruptible, by the word of God, which liveth and abideth for ever."
  },
  {
    "book": "1 Peter",
    "chapter": 1,
    "verse": 24,
    "text": "For all flesh\nis as grass, and all the glory of man as the flower of grass. The grass withereth, and the flower thereof falleth away:"
  },
  {
    "book": "1 Peter",
    "chapter": 1,
    "verse": 25,
    "text": "But the word of the Lord endureth for ever. And this is the word which by the gospel is preached unto you."
  },
  {
    "book": "Revelation",
    "chapter": 19,
    "verse": 1,
    "text": "And after these things I heard a great voice of much people in heaven, saying, Alleluia; Salvation, and glory, and honour, and power, unto the Lord our God:"
